Mirabelli on Suso: &quot;What I've said for Romagnoli and Bonaventura is the same for Suso. He made a joke in London (when he mentioned the release clause and that attention can be taken away from Donnarumma). This goes for everybody else too.&quot;<br />
<br />
Mirabelli on Suso: &quot;We are talking, we are Milan, there are many very important players who would like to wear our shirt. As long as he has the desire. On our part we do. If Suso or anyone else no longer wants to wear our shirt, it's normal for us to consider offers/requests.&quot;
